      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "OKLAHOMA BALE (2) was sent out long odds last time but charged out of the boxes with a fast early sectional and gave a sight before being swallowed up late, finishing a 3.5 lengths fourth (29.86) over 515m at this track. Ready to return to form. PAW OTIS (3) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fifth (30.06) in a Grade 5 at this track. Better than last start and can bounce back. PAW IMPERIAL (1) jumped from this box last time and placed in a Grade 5 at this track over 515m, finishing second (29.75). Has a very consistent record off this same box, including three wins and six placings from 15 starts. Expected to feature. CHAMPAGNE CUDDLE (7) should be thereabouts after filling a top-three spot most recently.",
